stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Requested: @request-author creates request
    Requested --> ArchitectureProposed: @spec-reviewer creates proposal
    ArchitectureProposed --> Approved: @architecture-approver auto-approves
    ArchitectureProposed --> Rejected: Rejected or not pursued

    Approved --> ImplementationReviewed: @implementation-reviewer confirms
    ImplementationReviewed --> Implementing: @spec-coder codes
    Implementing --> Verified: Tests pass
    Verified --> Closed: Autocommit / merge

    Rejected --> [*]
    Closed --> [*]

    note right of ArchitectureProposed: Auto-chain from @request-author
    note right of Approved: No human approval prompt needed
    note right of Verified: @test-reviewer must pass
